title: Left and Right Justify
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

* Add characters to a string until reaches a defined length.
* Useful for command line output justification.

```ruby
"Hello".ljust(30, "#")
#=> "Hello#########################"
```

```ruby
"Hello".rjust(30, "#")
#=> "#########################Hello"
```